law.history: Repealed 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 363, sec. 11, effective July 15, 1994. -- Repealed and reenacted 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 476, Pt. V, sec. 592, effective July 13, 1990. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 384, sec. 569, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 76, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Computer Services for the Blind Corporation.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/94). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 363 prevails over its amendment in 1994 Ky. Acts chs. 209 and 469.
